# At the end of a conversation or workflow, before your final summary:

- In a loop until everything is good:
    - Run `cargo clippy` and fix any issues
    - Run `cargo test` and fix any issues
    - PLEASE BE AWARE: stubbing out tests, marking tests as ignored, removing tests. test scumming with
        "assert True" and removing or commenting out failing code _does not count as fixing it_.
    - Just keep on trying, one test after another until everything is fixed. Eventually you'll get there...
    - I BELIEVE IN YOU!
